name: PhotoPrompts
0:
”Alexa, open photo prompts”
”Alexa, start photo prompts”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: photo prompts
des:
These are fun and creative photo prompts. Next time you are stuck trying to think of what to photograph, just ask Alexa for a suggestion. You can say, "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. 

This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
